# Enterprise business plan (SyncScript + Cursor)

When planning **product strategy**, **roadmap**, **go-to-market**, or **large refactors** that affect syncscript.app positioning:

1. Read **`SESSION_START.md`** and **`MEMORY.md`** (quick context first).
2. If present in the repo, read **`BUSINESS_PLAN.md`** (exported from Dashboard → Enterprise → **Plan** tab → “Copy markdown”) or ask the operator to paste the latest export.
3. Prefer the **in-app** source of truth (Supabase-backed Enterprise Plan tab); the markdown file is a **mirror** for Cursor and git.

Do not paste PATs or `sspat_*` tokens into chat. Use Settings → Privacy → Cursor / MCP tokens and env vars only.
